    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of an order containing small moth-like insects having two pairs of hairy membranous wings, closely related to moths and butterflies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
